</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PRESIDENT-MCCAIN?-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
QUIXOTIC JOHN MCCAIN: TILTING AT WINDMILLS _ AND THE WHITE HOUSE?  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Arizona)   (This excellent 1,050-word ``separate buy'' profile is from the
current (week beginning 13 June 1998) Economist magazine.)  
  
