<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980612.0077 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-12 09:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6148 &Cx1f; tad-z
r i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-DEVELOPING-CO     06-12 1896
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CLINTON-DEVELOPING-CO </SLUG>
