decorated by a different designer. (Grantham, Palm Beach Post)
MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   HIDDEN-DISNEY _ LAKE BUENA VISTA, Fla. _ Ahhh . . . it's a whole
new Disney World: Find bliss at quiet gardens, spa. (Lomartire,
Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   IDEA-HOUSE _ ORLANDO, Fla. _ Steal away from Disney and drop by
Southern Living's Idea House. (Van de Water, Palm Beach Post)
MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   RELIGION
</P>
<P>
   RELIGION-MUSIC _ The pleasures of 4HIM's ``Obvious'' are indeed
obvious. This Christian Contemporary band's new CD is filled with
vocal harmonies and hook-laden songs. (Blake, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
