   &UR; NATIONAL GENERAL &LR;  (``a'' code)
</P>
<P>
   MASS-CHILD-ABUSE (Cambridge, Mass.) _ A judge today ordered a
new trial for the woman who was convicted more than 10 years ago of
abusing children at her family's Fells Acres Day Care Center. In a
decision that could have implications for hundreds of child abuse
cases around the nation, Superior Court Judge Isaac A. Borenstein
said that the child abuse trial of Cheryl Amirault LeFave was
