<P>
   DELAHOYA _ The billboard showing a bare-chested Oscar De La Hoya
is the first indication that El Paso has an obsession with the
world champion boxer. By the time his private jet touched El Paso
soil, the hysteria had already begun. De La Hoya defends his WBC
welterweight championship Saturday night against Patrick
Charpentier. (Cantu, Austin American-Statesman) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
