   JOHN-PAUL (Los Angeles) _ Profile on women's apparel maker John
Paul Richard Inc., the Los Angeles-based company which was named
the nation's fastest-growing small business in a fourth annual
ranking by Entrepreneur magazine and Dun &AMP; Bradstreet. By Enrique
Rivero. (Will move in the ``f'' financial news file.)
</P>
