   NETCOM-IPO (Los Angeles) _ The computer testing equipment maker
Netcom Inc. has filed to hold an initial public offering in which
it will sell 20 percent of its business at an asking price of
$148.8 million. By Ben Sullivan. (Will move in the ``f'' financial
news file.) &QL;
